HEADWORD: cramped
<hw>cramped</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>inconveniently small; restricting
movement; -- of living quarters or workspace; <as>as, <ex>cramped</ex>
quarters; a <ex>cramped</ex> office</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> constricted, inconvenient, uncomfortably
small.</syn>⟦br⟧
